	(text "MCLK (Master Clock) signal, can only be generated by the ESP32 on GPIOs 0, 1 or 3.\nBut the ESP32 cannot generate two different frequencies (50MHz for Ethernet and ~12MHz for Audio) from the APLL simultaneously -> Active Crystal Oscillator"
